Alias myK0  K0
Alias anti-myK0 anti-K0
ChargeConj myK0 anti-myK0

# Need to define B0 mass eigenstates for VSS_BMIX model
Define dm 0.510e12

# Set the Upsilon(4S) to decay entirely into our signal B's
Decay Upsilon(4S)
1.0 B0 anti-B0 B0sig anti-B0sig VSS_BMIX dm;
Enddecay

# Set the signal side B decay, need the other side to decay generically for tagging
Decay B0sig
1.0 myK0 nu_e anti-nu_e PHOTOS PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B0sig
#
#
Decay myK0
1.0000 K_S0         PHOTOS PHSP ;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-myK0


# Signal EOF
End
